        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients undergoing an elective orthopedic knee- or hip replacement

          -  Participation based on informed consent

          -  &gt; 18 years old and &lt; 85 years old

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  BMI 18.5 &gt; x &lt; 40

